<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Site Unavailable</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f8f8f8;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            padding: 30px;
            max-width: 480px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #d9534f;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .contact {
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Site Locked</h1>
        <p>This website is currently unavailable because it has not been paid for.</p>
        <p>Please contact your developer to unlock and restore the site.</p>
        <p class="contact">Developer Contact: <br> <strong>+254 XXX XXX XXX</strong></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
